HEADWORD: Nuance
<hw>Nu`ance"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A shade of difference; a delicate gradation.</def>⟦br⟧
